{"tid":541562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指浸大「強制普通話考試」涉歧視　議員再去信平機會促跟進","createTime":"2018-01-26T14:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-27T06:59:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76cbe0a22037056c3c19e8de2ac90e787331bb48","tid":541562,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-25-2018/43749\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-25-2018%2F43749&d=zXBzb8A%2FFZ0woOaTik%2FBGjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1e3533bf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-25-2018/43749</a><br />\n<br />\n香港浸會大學將普通話能力列為畢業要求，涉歧視本地學生，熱血公民議員鄭松泰曾去信平等機會委員會要求調查，但至1月25日仍未見回覆，鄭松泰因此再去信平機會要求跟進。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰在信中指責浸大不但無審視「強制普通話考試」是否歧視本地學生，反而轉移視線，將爭議焦點放在學生情緒態度上，甚至以講粗口為由，繞過紀律聆迅程序將反對學生停學，鄭松泰促請平機會安排展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰1月17日曾去信平等機會委員會，指浸會大學將普通話能力列為畢業要求涉種族歧視，浸大將對本地學生施行更多的畢業要求，甚至自動豁免對大陸學生與外地生的粵語及普通話能力要求，等如優待非本地學生。"},{"pid":"325a7737dbe1d0a2a3eef57868c859ddf1189289","tid":541562,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3ae58482ac093f7e6d7bf4e24ae90d91acd1c7","tid":541562,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"希望重回正軌。"},{"pid":"b64f5764e49e3b0999fb1d935005ea290b7f495e","tid":541562,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cead68e0db399c4dfbb2ae92a5d7998266afb4","tid":541562,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 